Description:
    Generates a CafeCar resource: model, migration, route, controller, and
    Pundit policy. Field arguments use the ordinary Rails model-generator
    syntax and become permitted attributes in the generated policy.

Example:
    bin/rails generate cafe_car:resource admin/invoices total:decimal client:references

    Key application files:
        app/models/admin/invoice.rb
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXXXXXXXX_create_admin_invoices.rb
        app/controllers/admin/invoices_controller.rb
        app/policies/admin/invoice_policy.rb

    It also adds `resources :invoices` inside `namespace :admin` in
    config/routes.rb. The model step delegates to Rails' model generator, so it
    also creates the namespace, model test, and fixture files configured by the
    host application.
